{"tid":2198543,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]點解呢個年代冇曬瘦底學生妹存在","createTime":"2020-09-11T12:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T02:29:06.000Z","uid":373544,"like":13,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0a15943936e907e949a6a8134236f1e808eede6b","tid":2198543,"uid":373544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"以前睇開學生妹 好多都係瘦底<br />\n骨架偏細 手臂幼 小女人類型 惹人憐愛 想保護類型<br />\n當然講緊個胸唔好平曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前好易見到腿幼j腳 大腿有啲肉 腰幼幼嘅學生妹<br />\n唔係得骨嗰款啦 入嚟想拗瘦女唔正嘅肥婆可以死返出去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面啲圖有範例<br />\n但依家腿幼學生妹成為極稀有品種<br />\n去學校區域走返轉 啲學生妹隻腳好多都偏粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲係又短又粗 明明上身都唔係肥 <br />\n一係個人橫 大大隻<br />\n然後有班係以前嚟講算粗腳嘅女 係依家都可以算腳幼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會用蘿蔔形容呢班𡃁妹對腳<br />\n條腰就算有皮帶勒住 都睇得出唔係瘦底<br />\n講緊係街行一轉都唔太見到瘦底學生妹<br />\n成日話港女贏係有條好j嘅腳到<br />\n但呢批j腳港女似乎係8-90後 即係細個就係瘦底學生妹嗰班女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學生妹明明應該要瘦 冇咩贅肉咁<br />\n先有嗰種青春嘅味道<br />\n只有年紀漸大嘅中女先會有贅肉<br />\n瘦嘅女人（有一定程度嘅波）先可以符合窈窕淑女入面解做美麗賢淑嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先可以激發本君子嘅保護慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩肉地先好嘅說話真係啲肥婆用嚟帶風向<br />\n你16歲嗰陣已經有40歲嘅身型 我娶完你返屋企 擺你擺到40歲嗰陣你咪變北姑肥大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母啦我不如<br />\n話有肉先好屌 但人地苗條得嚟大髀都有肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同時有你冇嘅腰<br />\n相反搵個瘦底學生妹拍拖結婚 佢就真係40歲先變40歲應有嗰種肉地韻味身形啦<br />\n屌過肥又屌過瘦都知 女上時 得瘦（非洗衫板 大髀又有返啲肉）嘅女人先有條蛇腰扭啊扭 真係屌緊一個動人嘅女子嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：好憎肥婆<br />\n<br />\n以前啲學生妹：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QBbAVD4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQBbAVD4.png&h=aaaa7ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bfJvKxp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbfJvKxp.png&h=a63439ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iAVxXSq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiAVxXSq.png&h=7cf2e2da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KKtcdqM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKKtcdqM.png&h=1fd0b0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QkverLN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkverLN.png&h=67e498d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89acb15d76fbf1fcfb99b0475ba360293f7b51af","tid":2198543,"uid":201604,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"肥婆將會 全！面！進！場！"},{"pid":"c486ee6cf6ab21b202ee029b12582fa47aa6ee87","tid":2198543,"uid":373544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89acb15d76fbf1fcfb99b0475ba360293f7b51af","tid":2198543,"uid":201604,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"肥婆將會 全！面！進！場！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0b95ced08c197fdb9530fc68c7f46bdf3adae2","tid":2198543,"uid":371165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0a15943936e907e949a6a8134236f1e808eede6b","tid":2198543,"uid":373544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"以前睇開學生妹 好多都係瘦底<br />\n骨架偏細 手臂幼 小女人類型 惹人憐愛 想保護類型<br />\n當然講緊個胸唔好平曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前好易見到腿幼j腳 大腿有啲肉 腰幼幼嘅學生妹<br />\n唔係得骨嗰款啦 入嚟想拗瘦女唔正嘅肥婆可以死返出去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面啲圖有範例<br />\n但依家腿幼學生妹成為極稀有品種<br />\n去學校區域走返轉 啲學生妹隻腳好多都偏粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea